---
title: Buffalo Chicken Flatbread with Creamy Ranch Sauce
description: If there’s one thing we can agree on here, it’s that buffalo chicken and ranch are an almost-perfect pair. When you take that tried-and-true combo and put it on a flatbread (along with an almost-instant tomato sauce and fresh mozzarella), well, you’ve got yourself a perfectly perfect meal.
